 101.69-82.29 184-184 184zm0-312c-70.69 0-128 57.31-128 128s57.31 128 128 128 128-57.31 128-128-57.31-128-128-128zm0 192c-35.29 0-64-28.71-64-64s28.71-64 64-64 64 28.71 64 64-28.71 64-64 64z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">We value what children achieve rather than focus on their failures.<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-bullseye\" viewBox=\"0 0 496 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M248 8C111.03 8 0 119.03 0 256s111.03 248 248 248 248-111.03 248-248S384.97 8 248 8zm0 432c-101.69 0-184-82.29-184-184 0-101.69 82.29-184 184-184 101.69 0 184 82.29 184 184 0 101.69-82.29 184-184 184zm0-312c-70.69 0-128 57.31-128 128s57.31 128 128 128 128-57.31 128-128-57.31-128-128-128zm0 192c-35.29 0-64-28.71-64-64s28.71-64 64-64 64 28.71 64 64-28.71 64-64 64z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">We also believe in the need to nurture and develop our staff both professionally and personally. Since they are the one that create the climate in which our children will learn.<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/ul>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>About Us Our goal is to continue to produce well rounded students who will be able to compete anywhere in the world. We shall continue to teach good character by modelling and fostering compassion, respect, responsibility and integrity. In addition, our students will be challenged to pursue knowledge, creativity, and intellectual self reliance. We engage in community development and understand students\u2019 right and the responsibilities within a community that is itself part of the larger world. Our Mission Our mission at Pacific Academy is to teach, inspire, transform and nurture our students with knowledge and skills so that they grow to become responsible young adults who can meet the challenges of the 21st\u00a0century with confidence, persistence and resilience that will make them stand out wherever they may find themselves. Our Vision To create one of the state\u2019s most effective schools helping secondary students prepare for and be accepted into top post secondary institutions. School Philosophy We believe firmly that all our students can become successful learners. Hence, we are committed to helping them discover and pursue their interests and in the process, discover who they are and what kind of excellence they possesses. We believe that children learn best when they are actively engaged in their day to day learning and where they are given considerable responsibility for their studies. We believe that when children enjoy school, they will make accelerated progress towards intellectual maturity. We value what children achieve rather than focus on their failures. We also believe in the need to nurture and develop our staff both professionally and personally. Since they are the one that create the climate in which our children will learn.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":6,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-1442","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.2 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>About Us - eng - UPSS Schools<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"A leading educational institution in Nigeria, offering a holistic approach to learning from kindergarten to secondary levels.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"